= Before You Build Anything

Most ideas do not fail because people are lazy.

They fail because nobody tested demand early enough.

This workbook forces you to do the opposite.

In the next 30 days, you will talk to real people, test a real problem, make a tiny offer, and ask for real money.

If nobody pays, you stop or pivot.

If someone pays, you continue.

That is the entire game.

